sub_title: Chinese language trainer at Language Institute Regina Coeli ('De Nonnen van Vught')
summary:
I provide professional Chinese course at various levels, for individuals and groups, in-house, in-company and online (e.g. zoom, Skype). The courses can be given in English or Dutch. I’m specialized in personal tailor-made language training.
At present, I give lessons mainly at the language institute Regina Coeli (‘Nonnen van Vught’), open universities and online.
